Postcode,Anywhere,is,an,information,as,a,service,provider,offering,over,separate,web,services,covering,a,broad,range,of,business,efficiency,tools,for,address,and,data,capture,validation,and,cleansing,to,geo,coding,mapping,and,route,planning,and,optimisation,The,Email,validation,API,will,validate,email,addresses,at,the,point,of,capture,It,will,also,verify,the,existence,of,an,email,address,The,API,uses,a,number,of,protocols,including,REST,SOAP,and,XML,RPC,Responses,can,be,formatted,in,XML,JSON,CSV,HTML,and,PDF